'''1938年[[美國國家棒球名人堂|美國國家棒球名人堂]]票選'''是大聯盟第三屆的名人堂票選。票選方式大致和去年的票選方式相同。這年只有3個人入選名人堂，[[格羅佛·克里夫蘭·亞歷山大|格羅佛·克里夫蘭·亞歷山大]]是唯一一位經由全美棒球記者協會票選選出的入選者，<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/37545650/old_pete_in_hall_of_fame/ |title='Old Pete' in Hall of Fame |first=Bob |last=Considine |newspaper=[[Herald_&_Review|The Decatur Daily Review]] |location=[[Decatur,_Illinois|Decatur, Illinois]] |page=7 |date=January 19, 1938 |accessdate=October 20, 2019 |via=newspapers.com |archive-date=2019-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191020175923/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/37545650/old_pete_in_hall_of_fame/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>另外兩位分別是透過百年紀念委員會推薦的[[亞歷山大·卡特來特|亞歷山大·卡特來特]]和Henry Chadwick。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/37545914/oldtimers_added_to_hall_of_fame/ |title=Old-timers Added to Hall of Fame |agency=[[United_Press_International|UP]] |newspaper=[[St._Louis_Star-Times|The St. Louis Star and Times]] |page=20 |date=September 7, 1938 |accessdate=October 20, 2019 |via=newspapers.com |archive-date=2019-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191020175921/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/37545914/oldtimers_added_to_hall_of_fame/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

